WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.333 --> 00:00:03.501
The third and final flow is financials,

2
00:00:03.501 --> 00:00:05.985
or more specifically, cash.

3
00:00:05.985 --> 00:00:08.856
Traditionally, financial flow has been viewed

4
00:00:08.856 --> 00:00:12.504
as one directional upstream in the supply chain.

5
00:00:12.504 --> 00:00:16.168
In other words, financial flow is payment for goods,

6
00:00:16.168 --> 00:00:18.925
services, and orders received.

7
00:00:18.925 --> 00:00:21.542
A major impact of supply chain compression

8
00:00:21.542 --> 00:00:25.003
and faster order cycle times has been faster cash flow

9
00:00:25.003 --> 00:00:27.045
or structured contracts.

10
00:00:27.045 --> 00:00:30.741
The MSPV program is a national mandatory program

11
00:00:30.741 --> 00:00:33.510
that provides a customized distribution system

12
00:00:33.510 --> 00:00:36.149
to meet or exceed facility requirements

13
00:00:36.149 --> 00:00:38.813
by providing an efficient, cost effective

14
00:00:38.813 --> 00:00:42.107
just-in-time distribution catalog ordering process.

